<sect1 id="dir_1ca916e0b9fbc882dbfbd9e6594e5e22_1autotoc_md122">
<title>helios::engine::ecs</title><para>Core Entity-Component-System architecture for the helios game engine.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1ca916e0b9fbc882dbfbd9e6594e5e22_1autotoc_md123">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the foundational classes for the composition-based game architecture. It separates data (Components) from behavior (Systems). Entity lifecycle and world management are provided by <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world" kindref="compound">helios.engine.runtime.world</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
</sect1>
